  m_Name: Step 7
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  stepNumber: 7
  stepTitle: Data Monitoring and Recording
  stepDescription: "Record all readings using the Data Recorder on the control panel.\r\nThe
    Data Recorder displays the following parameters:\r\no REF1\r\nReference value
    from the Level Transmitter (Reference Unit)\r\no UUT1\r\nMeasurement value from
    the Unit Under Test (Level Transmitter)\r\no UUT1 Bypass\r\nMeasurement value
    from the UUT bypass line\r\no PT1\r\nPressure Transmitter reading (if applicable)\n\r\nRecord
    all readings for:\r\no All 5 calibration points (0% \u2013 100%)\r\no All 3 runs
    (increasing, decreasing, increasing)"
